Feature: Add a new address
  Scenario: Adding a new address

    Given Go to the website
    And Click on Sign In Tab
    And type to "email" and "password"
    And Click on Sign In Button
    And Click on My Addresses Button
    And Click on Add a new address Button
    And Type to "address" and "city" and "postcode" and "mobile" and "title"
    And Click on Save button


